title: Freddie Gibbs - Baby Face Killa (2012) (iTunes Rip)
description:
Baby Face Killa is a mixtape by American rapper Freddie Gibbs. It was released on September 25, 2012.[5] It is the first installment of the Gangsta Grillz series featuring Gary, Indiana based Freddie Gibbs. The mixtape was announced shortly after the release of the previous street album Cold Day In Hell. There are 18 tracks on the street album and additional bonus tracks on the deluxe edition that were released on iTunes. The mixtape features guest appearances from Pharrell Williams, Dana Williams, Z-Ro, Young Jeezy, Slick Pulla, Ea$y Money, YG, Dom Kennedy, SpaceGhostPurrp, Krayzie Bone, Jadakiss, Jay Rock, Wayne Blazed, Curren$y, Problem, G-Wiz, D-Edge, Hit Skrewface & Kirko Bangz.
